Did you meet him?

780
01:01:48,227 --> 01:01:50,849
Yeah, I met him, but...

781
01:01:51,898 --> 01:01:53,357
What's wrong, son?

782
01:01:53,566 --> 01:01:57,065
It's not how we thought
it was, Dad.

783
01:01:57,236 --> 01:02:00,072
