- Testify, sister!

946
01:14:36,329 --> 01:14:38,784
- Charge!
- Charge!

947
01:15:02,021 --> 01:15:04,512
<i>Oh, no! He's got
a steel chair.</i>

948
01:15:06,526 --> 01:15:10,226
